public class FormDetailDataGrid<T extends Selectable>
extends com.google.gwt.user.cellview.client.DataGrid<T>
implements ResourceAware

A custom data grid

This class, extends DataGrid, and on the row click, appends the given widget to the table. This is very useful for the grid containig forms. The mandatory params are:
  • ProvidesKey keyProvider, as for standard DataGrid
  • List of values, holded by the grid
  • FormDetailDataGrid.RowDetailWidget detail, that will be appended to the clicked row
  • An instance of the object used as empty row container

Author:
Alessandro Casolla
